\[
MRTS_{LK} = \frac{MPL}{MPK} = \frac{\frac{1}{4} (K-1)^{\frac{1}{4}} L^{-\frac{3}{4}}}{\frac{1}{4} K^{-\frac{3}{4}} L^{\frac{1}{4}}} = \frac{(K-1)^{\frac{1}{4}}}{K^{-\frac{3}{4}]} \cdot \frac{L^{-\frac{3}{4}}}{L^{\frac{1}{4}}}
